N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6654.2 - Outreach, training and coordination requirements

State Regulations

Service providers must comply with any outreach, training
and coordination requirements established by the area agency. All workers
delivering services must be appropriately qualified, selected, trained and
supervised as specified in this Part. Notes
